title: Tahm Kench Theme - Piano Cover!

embed.description: I present to you my piano cover for Tahm Kench's login music! Well this one got delayed a bit. I had been able to play this weeks ago, but I kept changing it, adding a few more notes and chords here and there, and every change I made meant I had to relearn parts, so it took a lot longer than it should have.

body:
Here is my rendition of Tahm Kench's Login Theme on piano!
I have more piano covers coming, so stay tuned!

replies.body: I love it! Great work m8!

not my thing, but good effort none-the less :)
